table_caption: Comparison of physical, cooking, and eating quality indicators of rice samples obtained from respondents by location (Famy and Sta Maria, Laguna, Philippines) using the Z-test.
table_foot: Note: Values presented are means and standard deviations (in parentheses).At p < 0.05, attributes with Z < -1.96 or Z > 1.96 are significantly different between the locations.
